### Create a new portfolio
POST http://localhost:3000/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "name": "Growth Portfolio",
  "initial_cash": 10000
}

### Get all portfolios
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolios

### Get portfolio by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}

### Buy asset
POST http://localhost:3000/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "buy",
  "asset_type": "stock",
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "units": 10,
  "price_per_unit": 150
}

### Sell asset
POST http://localhost:3000/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "sell",
  "asset_type": "stock",
  "symbol": "AAPL",
  "units": 5,
  "price_per_unit": 160
}

### List transactions for a portfolio
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/transactions
